| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6273 — Recovery Inhibition (BrainCipher)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7d3bc858-6ddc-556b-a969-398f22ee22e2"
